<BaseHead 
title="Refund Policy | Petstellation"
description="Refund Policy for Petstellation digital products."
/>

<Header />

<main class="legal-page">

<h1>Refund Policy</h1>

<p>Last updated: April 2026</p>

<p>
All products sold on Petstellation are digital downloads. Because of the
intangible nature of digital goods, all sales are generally final.
</p>

<h2>No Returns</h2>

<p>
Once a digital product has been downloaded or accessed, it cannot be returned.
For this reason we typically do not offer refunds.
</p>

<h2>Exceptions</h2>

<p>
Refunds may be considered in the following situations:
</p>

<ul>
<li>You were charged multiple times for the same product.</li>
<li>The product file is corrupted or cannot be accessed.</li>
<li>You accidentally purchased the same item twice.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Contact for Refund Requests</h2>

<p>
If you believe your situation qualifies for a refund, please contact us within
7 days of purchase with your order details.
</p>

<p>
We will review the request and respond as soon as possible.
</p>

</main>

<Footer />
